# ── Secrets and environment files ────────────────────────────────────────────
# These files must never be baked into a build layer, even an intermediate one.
# A secret present in any layer of a multi-stage build can be extracted from
# the builder image unless that image is never pushed.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# ── VCS metadata ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitignore

# ── IDE and editor directories ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── OS artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Local build outputs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bin/
*.exe

# ── Test artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.test
*.out
coverage.html
coverage.out

# ── Go workspace files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
go.work
go.work.sum

# ── Claude Code local settings ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ── Documentation that adds no value to the build context ────────────────────
# docs/ contains generated Go source (docs.go) required at compile time — do not exclude it.
*.md
